list.comment:
changed Seedings in GetTourney to use the regualr tourney seedings and do string splitting to get the seed. Changed the docstring to reflect that.
Added docstring to bracket_visualizer. made the bracket image file a parameter with a default value. Added a check to make sure the bracket_dict input contains all the necessary bracket slots. Maybe I should move the whole function into GetTourney?

task.summary: creating a feature engineering class and new_implement shows it's use to get training and test data. Need to update the functions to accept filepaths for all the CSVs

changed training and test data output to be [diff in seed, diff in ELO, diff in ASM]. oh, also I implemented ASM(Adjusted Scoring Margin). Also added the websites for Offensive Quotient, Def. Quo., and ASM. Added a JPEG of a blank bracket. figured I could fill it in with openCV putText to create a printable bracket output with probabilities as a final output for the tournament
working on bracket visualization. the first round is in progress
vis_bracket2 is putting almost everything in the right places
vis_bracket2 works for all games except for the 2 finalists, the champion, and the weird 1st four games.
vis_bracket2 now does the whole bracket including the finals and the first4 playin games
bracket_visualizer works well. also puts the time and date on the bracket. saving is not working though
